        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> Per Verant, if a Pet outdamages your party, they get a cut of the exp.  When soloing, that means they get 1/2 the exp.  In a group, they have to outdamage all of you in order to get a share, otherwise they take none.</P><P><BR>--Fossil<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
