topic.gif" border=0>: THIS IS THE EDITING OPTION!!! If you mess-up, or forget something, or whatever, and would like to change something about your post - simply click this icon and you will be taken to a screen where you can make whatever changes you wish.</b><BR><img src="http://necro.eqclasses.com/icon_reply_topic.gif" border=0>: This is the button you push if you would like to reply to someone's post with a quote from it. This option will put the ENTIRE POST in quotes, so it is usually necessary (and easier on those with slow connections) to delete, cut/copy/paste and only leave the text that you wish to comment about.<BR><img src="http://necro.eqclasses.com/icon_delete_reply.gif" border=0>: this is the icon you press if you wish to delete a post - say your comp lags a bit and you spam the "Post" button for it to work - then all of the sudden you have 18 messages clogging up the forums, this is a bad thing and this is how you fix it.</P><P>The above is not all of the possible icons, however it is most of them - the others include one's that will allow you to send the person an instant message with AIM (<img src="http://necro.eqclasses.com/icon_aim.gif" border=0>) or to ICQ message (<img src="http://online.mirabilis.com/scripts/online.dll?icq=123669838&img=5" border=0>) or even a Yahoo! Message (<img src="http://necro.eqclasses.com/icon_yahoo.gif" border=0>) and I'm sure there are others around I haven't seen/don't remember.</P><P><BR><img src="http://www.imahosting.com/sigs/azumaan1.jpg" border=0><br><font size=1><b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=54401" target="_blank">Azumaan</a></b><br>30 Erudite Necromancer<br>Silver Faith<br>Mithaniel Marr</font id=size1></P><P>Edited by - Azumaan Necromaan on 04/10/2002  16:24:06<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
